OL,5, Leaders of the world's largest Baptist 
OL,6, denomination covered up sex abuse by   
OL,7, clergy for years and vilified          
OL,8, survivors, an internal report says.    
OL,10,FThe seven-month investigation found    
OL,11,Fthat survivors had come forward over   
OL,12,Ftwo decades about abusers within the   
OL,13,FSouthern Baptist Convention (SBC).     
OL,15,FBut their pleas for intervention were  
OL,16,Fmet with "resistance, stonewalling, and
OL,17,Feven outright hostility" by officials. 
OL,19,FWith 13 million members, SBC is the    
OL,20,Flargest Protestant body in the US.     
